---
title: Cal Smart Salmon and Bulgur Bowls with Tangy Herb Sauce and Roasted Veggies
description: Slightly smoky, herby and chock full of veggies, this calorie-smart meal has it all. Pan-seared salmon sit over bulgur, roasted veggies and baby spinach, and herby yogurt sauce brings the whole dish together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-saumon-et-de-boulgour-335c044d.jpg
